<lyrics>[V1]
 gẖyrn qlby nʿm yạrby .. kymạ yṣbḥ mtẖl qlbk
 ạ̉nt ạlfkẖạry ậty ạ̹lyk .. kẖzf ạ̉ny byn ydyk
